---
import LearnBtn from "../../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import Whatsbtn from "../../unitComponents/Whatsbtn.astro";
import Logo from "../../../assets/logos/LogoTriasoMX.svg";
import Cabins from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/SpareCabine.webp";
import img1 from "../../../assets/images/Maintenance/userManual.webp";
import img2 from "../../../assets/images/Maintenance/maintenance1.webp";
import img3 from "../../../assets/images/Maintenance/tolvas.webp";
import img4 from "../../../assets/images/Maintenance/banner2.webp";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section
  class="w-full font-bold text-grisT mt-28 flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
>
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-end">MAINTENANCE</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br />

  <div class="w-full flex justify-center px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
        Triaso’s maintenance services are designed to keep your equipment
        operating at peak performance, minimizing downtime and maximizing
        efficiency.
        <br />Our team of expert technicians, operators, and engineers
        meticulously inspects, services, and optimizes every component of your
        asphalt plant.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full bg-[url(/Gallery/drum-mixer.webp)] bg-cover bg-center h-[350px] md:h-[700px] mt-16"
  >
    <div class="w-full h-full flex justify-center bg-white/70 py-10">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 px-8 gap-16 justify-center items-center max-w-7xl h-full"
      >
        <div class="w-full col-span-1">
          <Whatsbtn />
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 w-full text-end">
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-black">24/7 CUSTOMER SERVICE</h1>
          <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">
            OUR TEAM IS AVAILABLE AROUND THE CLOCK, READY TO ASSIST YOU AT ANY
            TIME, EVEN ON WEEKENDS AND HOLIDAYS.
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center px-8 bg-blueMain py-6 md:py-16 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl">
      <p class="text-sm md:text-lg">
        Comprehensive phone support for maintenance and fault diagnosis is
        available to all equipment owners—both original and
        subsequent—throughout the product’s entire lifespan. Our experts are
        ready to guide you through solutions and help ensure your asphalt plant
        operates at peak efficiency for years to come.
      </p><br />
      <p class="text-sm md:text-lg">
        Additionally, we have a team of skilled technicians ready to provide
        prompt on-site assistance for future relocations or servicing,
        guaranteeing uninterrupted equipment performance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full bg-[url(/Gallery/banner2.webp)] bg-cover bg-center h-[450px] md:h-[700px]"
  >
    <div
      class="w-full h-full bg-white/70 px-8 py-16 text-black flex justify-center"
    >
      <div class="max-w-7xl flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">USER MANUAL</h1><br />
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
          We provide the most complete user manual in the industry for equipment
          installation and maintenance. This allows you to independently handle
          future installations and perform full maintenance with confidence.
        </p><br />
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
          <Image src={img1} alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-blueMain text-center">
      Technical and Professional Focus
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="w-full col-span-1 px-8">
      <Image src={Cabins} alt="" class="rounded-2xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full col-span-1">
      <div class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-redBg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-white text-xl md:text-3xl">
          Available anytime for immediate <br />equipment support
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 justify-center items-center px-8"
  >
    <div class="w-full py-10 flex flex-col gap-3">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-blueMain text-lg md:text-xl">
        Tailored upgrades
      </h2>
      <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
        We evaluate your current setup and suggest only the upgrades that will
        truly improve your plant’s performance, safety, and compliance.
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-grisT text-lg md:text-xl">
        Compatibility guaranteed
      </h2>
      <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
        We adapt our solutions to fit your existing systems, regardless of the
        original brand or age of the equipment.
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-redBg text-lg md:text-xl">
        Structural and mechanical reinforcements
      </h2>
      <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
        We rebuild worn-out parts, reinforce critical components, and install
        updated systems to extend your equipment’s lifespan.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-normal">
      <Image src={img2} alt="" class="rounded-lg w-1/2 lg:w-full" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl flex justify-center items-center pb-5">
    <Image src={img3} alt="" class="w-3/4 rounded-lg" />
  </div>
  <div class="w-full bg-grisT relative h-[300px]">
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 w-full"
    >
      <Image src={Logo} alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center h-full">
      <div
        class="max-w-7xl h-full px-8 text-white text-sm md:text-lg relative z-20 justify-center flex flex-col items-center"
      >
        <p class="">
          With a proactive approach to maintenance, we work to extend the
          lifespan of your equipment and ensure consistent reliability.
        </p><br />
        <p class="">
          Backed by rigorous quality control and advanced engineering
          techniques, our systems are built for seamless, long-term
          operation—giving you the confidence to focus on your projects without
          unexpected interruptions
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full text-center my-6 md:my-16">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-blueMain text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      Triaso® Spare Parts
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full px-4 mb-16 flex justify-center">
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl bg-[url(/Gallery/Boxes.webp)] bg-cover bg-center md:h-[550px] rounded-2xl"
    >
      <div
        class="w-full h-full bg-black/70 text-white text-sm md:text-lg text-center flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-4 md:px-16 pt-5 lg:pt-0 rounded-2xl"
      >
        <p>
          No other asphalt plant manufacturer in the world produces as many of
          its own components as Triaso.
        </p><br />
        <p>
          This vertical integration allows us to offer unmatched service,
          warranty coverage, and direct support—both from our factory in Mexico
          and our distributor in the United States.
        </p><br />
        <p>
          We ship spare parts worldwide to ensure your production never stops.
          Every part is backed by guaranteed quality, competitive pricing, and
          fast delivery times.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 md:mt-16 mb-10 lg:mb-0 flex justify-center">
          <LearnBtn />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
